    <div class="callout-text component-text">
        <p>The American Academy of Dermatology gratefully acknowledges the support from <a href="https://www.ortho-dermatologics.com/" title="">Ortho Dermatologics</a>.<br>



</p><p><a href="https://www.ortho-dermatologics.com/"><img src="//images.ctfassets.net/1ny4yoiyrqia/51p72XILXfbhJdOVbDeYPs/72d603f1cb44ad8fdaada6cc0fa42a14/OrthoDerm.png" alt="Footer&gt;Support&gt;Corporate&gt;ortho-dermatologics" /></a></p>

